title: Codicons (VS Code)
info: Creative Commons-licensed [iconset](https://github.com/microsoft/vscode-codicons/) used in [Visual Studio Code](https://code.visualstudio.com/) from Microsoft.

title: Feather
info: [Feather](https://feathericons.com/) is a collection of simply beautiful open source icons. Each icon is designed on a 24x24 grid with an emphasis on simplicity, consistency, and flexibility.

title: Teenyicons
info: Tiny [minimal 1px icons designed](https://github.com/teenyicons/teenyicons/) to fit in the smallest places.
